<p><strong>A Surprise Encounter with Crispy Sex Pirates</strong><br />
<strong>Author:</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1735419); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1735419&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1600579078" alt="Lt Flops" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1735419)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1735419); return false;">Lt Flops</a></span></p>
<p>This is a tale for <strong>Day 1</strong> of the <strong><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/144-hour-jam-contest" target="_blank">144-Hour Jam Contest</a></strong>. The theme was &quot;Shaggy Dog story&quot;.</p>
